Survey.dc:title: My Care Overview
Survey.introText:
You are invited to participate in a survey to provide TuAnalyze with your "Care Overview". These data will help put into context the A1c data that the community is sharing through the application.

Survey responses will be aggregated for analysis as part of TuAnalyze research. Individual identity will be protected. You can review your responses to this survey, once completed, in the TuAnalyze app. Your survey responses will not be visible to others.

After you complete the survey, please review and update your A1c data in order to keep the app current.

Thank you for participating! Your involvement matters.
Survey.completedMessage: Go to My Profile to update your hbA1c.
Survey.dc:creator: Skyler
